# 7. Quick Rules

| Situation | Use |
|-----------|-----|
| Font Size | rem |
| Width | % |
| Full Screen Height | vh |
| Full Screen Width | vw |
| Borders | px |
| Icons | px |
| Padding/Margin | rem or px |
| Grid Layout | fr |

