# 10. Golden Rules

✅ Use **16px** as the default paragraph size.

✅ Prefer **rem** for fonts.

✅ Use **%** for responsive widths.

✅ Use **vh/vw** for full-screen sections.

✅ Use spacing in multiples of **4** or **8**.

✅ Maintain consistent spacing throughout the project.

✅ Build a reusable design system instead of guessing values.

---

# One-Line Memory Trick

- **px** → Fixed size
- **rem** → Scalable text & spacing
- **em** → Relative to parent
- **%** → Relative to parent width/height
- **vh** → Screen height
- **vw** → Screen width
- **fr** → Flexible grid space

> **Design first, size second. Think in relationships, not numbers.**
